title: $:/themes/jd/Material
author: JD
name: Material
readme:
Hello, this [[TW5|https://tiddlywiki.com/]] theme is inspired by Google's ''Material Design'' When updating, you might want to delete this config tiddler first: $:/themes/jd/Material/ConfigDB
the above shadow tiddler gets overwritten when tweaking this theme at the control panel You can always get the latest updates here: http://j.d.material.tiddlyspot.com/ Please report bugs / suggest anything here: https://github.com/jdjdjdjdjdjd/TW5-Material Google Groups discussion: https://groups.google.com/forum/#!topic/TiddlyWiki/qiS1Vs46EQw%5B1-25%5D My other TW5 stuff: http://j.d.tiddlyspot.com/
